            <history-note id="DLM286549"><amended-provision>Section 55(1)(ha)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>28 September 1993</amendment-date>, by section 3 of the <amending-leg>Gas Amendment Act 1993</amending-leg> (1993 No 144).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM286550"><amended-provision>Section 55(1)(ha)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>15 November 2000</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM77701">section 3</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Gas Amendment
